{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then-- and then we had one for the-- for the little kids, and then we had one for the teenagers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the teenagers, we sent back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them finally went onto BA, and BS, and a Master, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were completely responsible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very interesting, because I don't know if you know about ORT?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the ORT organization-- was-- I was the first one they contacted in Paris when they started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a big, big piece of land around the first house that I had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they asked me if I would be willing to let each child have a little piece of garden, and that they would show them what it means to grow-- for the seeds to grow, and for-- and they were-- this was one of the most fabulous ways that the kids started to forget.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they were going to work in their garden, they-- they couldn't wait to go the next day to see if one flower bloomed, or if one carrot came out, or if there were some peas.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was absolutely fantastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I was forever grateful to ORT for that, because it was fabulous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then also what they did in the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know-- they had workshops in most of the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they trained those people who were-- God knows what they were before they were deported.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they couldn't go back in the same-- in the same profession or whatever they were because they were going to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they couldn't start being a doctor, or a lawyer, or anything in Israel, not knowing the language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had to get a skill.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
